metadata.name: Checkshrooms
metadata.description: My twist on the iconic Checks - VV Edition by Jack Butcher. In the art world, derivatives play a vital role in keeping the original works of art relevant by inspiring new perspectives, interpretations, and extending their cultural impact. I hope this sparks your inner thoughts about the balance between technology and nature, and to encourage a greater appreciation for the natural world and its ability to adapt and thrive amidst the chaos of our rapidly evolving digital age.
